 717:Drivers/lvgl/src/indev/lv_indev.c **** /**
 718:Drivers/lvgl/src/indev/lv_indev.c ****  * Process a new point from LV_INDEV_TYPE_POINTER input device
 719:Drivers/lvgl/src/indev/lv_indev.c ****  * @param i pointer to an input device
