1685:Drivers/lvgl/src/indev/lv_indev.c **** /**
1686:Drivers/lvgl/src/indev/lv_indev.c ****  * Handle focus/defocus on click for POINTER input devices
1687:Drivers/lvgl/src/indev/lv_indev.c ****  * @param proc pointer to the state of the indev
